comments: Okogie (MIN) briefly places his arm on Dragic's (MIA) waist at the top of the key.
Butler (MIA) makes incidental contact with Hernangomez (MIN) during the rebound.
Hernangomez (MIN) makes marginal contact to the body of Dragic (MIA) at the end of the drive.
Dragic (MIA) slightly extends his arm into the upper body of Hernangomez (MIN) on the drive.
Beasley (MIN) is allowed to raise his left foot off the ground as long as he releases his dribble before his foot lands.
Adebayo (MIA) makes contact to the body of McLaughlin (MIN) on the drive.
McLaughlin (MIN) maintains a legal guarding position during Butler's (MIA) shot attempt.
Replay review of the foul called on Okogie (MIN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Okogie grabs and restricts Adebayo's arm on the rebound.
Layman (MIN) is firming up and makes slight contact to Jones Jr. (MIA) during the screen.
Jones Jr. (MIA) makes contact to the arm of Layman (MIN) during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Adebayo (MIA) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Okogie (MIN) during the screen.
Layman (MIN) makes contact to Butler's (MIA) arm during his shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) makes slight contact to McLaughlin's (MIN) body during his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Beasley (MIN) makes marginal contact to the body of Butler (MIA) at the end of the drive.
Russell (MIN) maintains a legal guarding position and cleanly blocks Butler (MIA) shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) commits a take foul on Layman (MIN).
Hernangomez (MIN) cleanly deflects the ball away from Butler (MIA) during the steal.
